  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Build Animated Fun Arcade games for your customers</strong></u><strong>  </strong><br>Crane Games, Coin Pushers, Bowling, Air Hockey, Dance Games, Hit Target Throwing Games, Pinball, Motorcycle Racing Game, Unlock the lock game, Lightgun game, Arcade Cabinet, Japanese styled arcade cabinet, Ball Drop Arcade Game, Coin Pusher, Ring Toss, Pong Game, Vortex Game, Bowling Game, Big Wheel Spin, Ticket Checker, Lots of furniture object...and more on release! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/9484c53901ecdbe2d6e6ab7e7b046fdd.avif?t=1774129070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras_big/9484c53901ecdbe2d6e6ab7e7b046fdd.avif?t=1774129070 width=800 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/81a3c0f590415cf5bf30b17dab159505.avif?t=1774129070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras_big/81a3c0f590415cf5bf30b17dab159505.avif?t=1774129070 width=800 height=124 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/23c6a308fa5ad961a1173f43149c8f16.avif?t=1774129070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras_big/23c6a308fa5ad961a1173f43149c8f16.avif?t=1774129070 width=800 height=136 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/ed0406d3555376e0c4dc78feddd81dda.avif?t=1774129070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras_big/ed0406d3555376e0c4dc78feddd81dda.avif?t=1774129070 width=800 heigh