0 height=450 /></span><strong></strong><br><u><strong>Create advertisements</strong></u>  <br>Drive in more customers with randomly generate advertisement campaigns, use your smarts to determine which ones will bring in the most profit. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/d305e18c9db76a77ed3d7138321899d2.avif?t=1774129070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras_big/d305e18c9db76a77ed3d7138321899d2.avif?t=1774129070 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><u><strong>Events</strong></u><br>Create events in your arcade light high score challenges, speed running, dance tournaments and more! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/43c1c1966bf5fa461e97461d817930c8.avif?t=1774129070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras_big/43c1c1966bf5fa461e97461d817930c8.avif?t=1774129070 width=800 height=416 /></span><br><br><strong><u>Staff</u></strong>Hire and manager staff to help customers, repair machines, upgrade machines and clean up the arcade!<strong><u></u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290450/extras/364a798a4510410f884da9df893a3044.avif?t=1774129070\" width=800 height=396 /></span><strong><u></u></strong><br><strong>Economy / Management </strong><br>Manage your finances in Arcade Manager by adjusting the costs per credits when guests enter the arcade. Set different credit costs per machine, adjust jackpot settings like the odds <br> <br><strong>Arcade Manager  </strong><br>Build and manage the arcade of your dreams in Arcade Manager! Start with a few machines, funky carpet, and sticky floors, then grow your business into a bustling entertainment hub, become a tycoon. of hitting a jackpot and the payout of the jackpot. Hire Staff each with different stats, like how fast they will repair/clean and how expensive they are. Events cost money and can be adjusted how big the event prize is. <br> </p>",
